wlanpi-shell-config (1.1.0) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Fix FZF integration for Debian bookworm (switch to traditional sourcing method)
  * Add root user configuration for consistent shell experience
  * Add vim directory setup (undodir and viminfo) with proper permissions
  * Add automatic .bashrc.d sourcing to .bashrc
  * Split ghostty terminal support into separate optional file
  * Match pi-gen shell configuration behavior

